1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 18]

2
00:00:30,738 --> 00:00:31,417
Darling.

3
00:00:31,578 --> 00:00:32,017
Darling.

4
00:00:32,018 --> 00:00:32,897
