8
00:00:39,138 --> 00:00:39,497
I did.

9
00:00:39,658 --> 00:00:40,097
I did.

10
00:00:45,098 --> 00:00:45,737
Youyi.

11
00:00:46,218 --> 00:00:47,497
Youyi, I've missed you so much.

12
00:00:47,498 --> 00:00:48,777
Let me kiss you first.

13
00:00:49,578 --> 00:00:50,577
Don't rush.

14
00:00:53,418 --> 00:00:54,456
Youyi, I...

15
00:00:54,457 --> 00:00:55,577
I've been longing for you...

16
00:00:58,418 --> 00:00:59,017
You can't even imagine

17
00:00:59,618 --> 00:01:01,577
