18
00:01:02,938 --> 00:01:04,497
I know you've suffered.

19
00:01:04,618 --> 00:01:06,417
But this is all temporary.

20
00:01:06,418 --> 00:01:07,617
We just need to wait a little longer.

21
00:01:07,898 --> 00:01:09,297
How much longer?

22
00:01:10,978 --> 00:01:12,897
Until I become head of the family.

23
00:01:12,978 --> 00:01:14,577
Youyi. Youyi.

24
00:01:15,898 --> 00:01:16,577
Youyi.

25
00:01:18,578 --> 00:01:19,897
I've missed you so much, Youyi.

26
00:01:20,218 --> 00:01:20,977
Youyi.

27
00:01:31,578 --> 00:01:32,737
Where are my clothes?

28
00:01:33,898 --> 00:01:35,497
What clothes?

29
