33
00:01:52,818 --> 00:01:53,977
Arrange police vehicle transfer for me.

34
00:01:54,218 --> 00:01:55,497
I'm leaving with the child tonight.

35
00:02:01,818 --> 00:02:03,217
The police transfer back then

36
00:02:03,498 --> 00:02:04,577
was ordered by Zhou Quan.

37
00:02:07,818 --> 00:02:09,097
Judging by the timing,

38
00:02:09,538 --> 00:02:10,577
the transfer occurred

39
00:02:10,898 --> 00:02:12,337
at dusk on New Year's Eve.

40
00:02:13,658 --> 00:02:14,577
At that exact time,

41
00:02:15,018 --> 00:02:16,937
my sister had just escaped from Zhou Yichen.

42
00:02:17,738 --> 00:02:19,377
Fourth Concubine doesn't have an alibi for the time of the crime,

43
00:02:20,258 --> 00:02:21,937
so she's not connected to my sister's death.

44
00:02:22,378 --> 00:02:24,097
So she was afraid her child would be exposed.

45
00:02:24,578 --> 00:02:25,577
She isn't coming home

46
00:02:25,578 --> 00:02:26,857
not because she's afraid of Father,

47
00:02:27,218 --> 00:02:28,257
but because she feels guilty.

48
00:02:29,018 --> 00:02:31,617
No wonder father transferred all property

49
00:02:31,618 --> 00:02:32,857
