58
00:02:55,738 --> 00:02:57,737
This decision might be inappropriate.

59
00:02:59,258 --> 00:03:00,697
What right does a lowly maid

60
00:03:00,738 --> 00:03:02,777
have to say what's appropriate?

61
00:03:03,378 --> 00:03:06,097
These are Zhou family elders and meritorious members.

62
00:03:06,378 --> 00:03:08,897
If they say tonight, then tonight it is.

63
00:03:10,378 --> 00:03:12,537
We support Fourth Concubine's decision too.

64
00:03:13,778 --> 00:03:15,497
If the eldest son doesn't come tonight,

65
00:03:15,498 --> 00:03:17,017
