Lin Youyi, two votes.

82
00:03:55,378 --> 00:03:56,097
Lin Youyi.

83
00:03:56,098 --> 00:03:56,617
Three votes.

84
00:03:57,098 --> 00:03:57,737
Lin Youyi.

85
00:03:58,098 --> 00:03:58,537
Four votes.

86
00:03:58,938 --> 00:03:59,617
Lin Youyi.

87
00:03:59,778 --> 00:04:00,497
Five votes.

88
00:04:00,738 --> 00:04:01,497
Lin Youyi.

89
00:04:01,618 --> 00:04:02,217
Six votes.

90
00:04:02,538 --> 00:04:04,657
It is my honor to announce

91
00:04:05,018 --> 00:04:05,937
that through this

92
00:04:06,178 --> 00:04:07,857
just and fair election,

93
00:04:08,458 --> 00:04:09,497
Ms. Lin Youyi

94
00:04:09,618 --> 00:04:11,377
will become the new...

95
