115
00:04:43,578 --> 00:04:43,977
This.

116
00:04:43,978 --> 00:04:44,577
Everyone,

117
00:04:44,658 --> 00:04:45,857
I have proof of the affair between

118
00:04:46,498 --> 00:04:47,777
Fourth Concubine

119
00:04:47,778 --> 00:04:48,857
