137
00:05:15,098 --> 00:05:16,137
Whether it's framed or not,

138
00:05:16,258 --> 00:05:17,337
why not try a blood mixing test?

139
00:05:17,338 --> 00:05:17,857
why not try a blood mixing test?

140
00:05:17,898 --> 00:05:19,137
[Zhou Yiruo and Zhou Yinan]

141
