144
00:05:35,618 --> 00:05:37,257
That'll silence the gossip.

145
00:05:37,858 --> 00:05:38,977
Yes.

146
00:05:39,258 --> 00:05:40,257
No test!

147
00:05:40,578 --> 00:05:41,337
Why should I?

148
00:05:41,338 --> 00:05:42,337
If we don't test today,

149
00:05:42,658 --> 00:05:43,497
