151
00:05:45,258 --> 00:05:46,497
The Zhou residence is surrounded

152
00:05:46,498 --> 00:05:47,137
by He family guards.

153
00:05:49,858 --> 00:05:50,577
Then let's test.

154
00:05:50,778 --> 00:05:51,457
Director Zhou,

155
00:05:51,578 --> 00:05:52,777
