164
00:06:06,978 --> 00:06:07,617
Yes.

165
00:06:21,858 --> 00:06:22,577
Director Zhou.

166
00:06:39,338 --> 00:06:39,897
It...

167
00:06:39,898 --> 00:06:40,977
