175
00:07:16,138 --> 00:07:17,337
Open your eyes wide and see clearly!

176
00:07:18,618 --> 00:07:19,977
The He family reserves

177
00:07:19,978 --> 00:07:22,137
permanent voting rights.

178
00:07:25,138 --> 00:07:26,257
You've finally come!

179
00:07:31,338 --> 00:07:32,857
This is the contract Zhou Huaiqian

180
00:07:32,858 --> 00:07:34,777
signed with our He family

181
00:07:34,898 --> 00:07:36,777
when acquiring our assets.

182
00:07:40,138 --> 00:07:41,137
Seeing your elder,

183
00:07:41,138 --> 00:07:42,377
how dare you remain seated?

184
00:07:42,658 --> 00:07:43,777
Stand up!

185
00:07:54,978 --> 00:07:57,337
Electing a family head is crucial...

186
00:07:58,338 --> 00:08:00,137
We must choose an auspicious day.

187
00:08:00,778 --> 00:08:02,657
Fourth Concubine is young and impulsive,

188
00:08:02,858 --> 00:08:04,137
but surely the rest of you

189
00:08:04,658 --> 00:08:06,457
aren't equally rash?

190
00:08:07,738 --> 00:08:09,097
Aren't you afraid Huaiqian might

191
00:08:09,498 --> 00:08:11,337
knock on your door in the dead of night?

192
00:08:16,378 --> 00:08:17,457
Since

193
00:08:17,578 --> 00:08:19,137
Matriarch He insists,

194
00:08:20,098 --> 00:08:20,897
