195
00:08:21,338 --> 00:08:21,777
Yes, yes!

196
00:08:21,778 --> 00:08:22,137
Agreed.

197
00:08:22,138 --> 00:08:23,257
In three days,

198
00:08:23,658 --> 00:08:24,577
we'll re-elect.

199
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:26,897
Yes.
- Absolutely.

200
00:08:35,218 --> 00:08:36,097
I swear

201
00:08:36,098 --> 00:08:36,897
that basin of water

202
00:08:36,898 --> 00:08:38,097
wasn't tampered with.

203
00:08:38,338 --> 00:08:39,697
I carried it the whole way.

204
00:08:39,778 --> 00:08:40,697
I don't suspect you.

205
00:08:41,338 --> 00:08:42,457
Nanxi, you may leave.

206
00:08:43,218 --> 00:08:43,897
Yes.

207
00:08:45,698 --> 00:08:47,297
The letter states it plainly.

208
00:08:47,778 --> 00:08:48,537
Otherwise, Fourth Concubine wouldn't have

209
00:08:48,538 --> 00:08:49,937
gone through such trouble to meet Zhou Quan

210
00:08:49,938 --> 00:08:50,897
to destroy it.

211
00:08:51,538 --> 00:08:52,777
Where did things go wrong?

212
00:08:54,298 --> 00:08:55,097
Actually,

213
00:08:55,098 --> 00:08:56,657
I suggested the blood test

214
00:08:56,898 --> 00:08:59,297
to see how they'd react.

215
00:09:00,578 --> 00:09:01,897
Because blood paternity testing

216
00:09:02,658 --> 00:09:03,697
is inherently unscientific.

217
00:09:04,698 --> 00:09:05,457
How would they react?

218
00:09:05,458 --> 00:09:06,177
Zhou Quan saw

219
00:09:06,178 --> 00:09:08,177
that his blood didn't mix with the child's.

220
00:09:08,338 --> 00:09:09,777
He stormed off in anger.

221
00:09:10,018 --> 00:09:11,577
This is an insult to me!

222
00:09:11,698 --> 00:09:12,897
It shows he believes

223
00:09:13,218 --> 00:09:14,937
the twins are his own.

224
00:09:15,178 --> 00:09:16,217
But the Fourth Concubine

225
00:09:16,218 --> 00:09:17,337
remained completely calm.

226
00:09:17,458 --> 00:09:18,337
Logically speaking,

227
00:09:18,418 --> 00:09:19,217
Zhou Quan

228
00:09:19,218 --> 00:09:20,577
is the Master's cousin.

229
00:09:20,898 --> 00:09:23,657
So this shouldn't be her expected result.

230
00:09:24,098 --> 00:09:25,017
You mean

231
00:09:25,338 --> 00:09:26,217
she already knew Zhou Quan's

232
00:09:26,538 --> 00:09:28,017
blood wouldn't mix with the child's?

233
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:29,937
Earlier in the garden,

234
00:09:30,098 --> 00:09:31,457
I noticed Miss Yinan

235
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:33,337
has a very rare condition

236
00:09:33,578 --> 00:09:34,937
called tritanopia.

237
00:09:37,218 --> 00:09:38,657
Do you want to pick this little red flower?

238
00:09:39,458 --> 00:09:40,817
I want that pink one.

239
00:09:41,578 --> 00:09:42,537
You mean this?

240
00:09:43,818 --> 00:09:44,937
Then what color is this?

241
00:09:45,098 --> 00:09:46,097
Blue.

242
00:09:46,778 --> 00:09:48,537
Your red dress today is very beautiful.

243
00:09:48,778 --> 00:09:50,537
I love red the most.

244
00:09:50,778 --> 00:09:51,897
Tritanopia.

245
00:09:52,938 --> 00:09:54,417
It's a genetic disorder

246
00:09:54,418 --> 00:09:55,897
that only affects girls.

247
00:09:56,418 --> 00:09:58,337
I've only heard of red-green color blindness.

248
00:09:58,338 --> 00:09:59,897
How is tritanopia different?

249
00:09:59,898 --> 00:10:01,017
Patients can accurately

250
00:10:01,018 --> 00:10:02,217
identify true red,

251
00:10:02,818 --> 00:10:03,937
but they mistake yellow

252
00:10:04,218 --> 00:10:05,217
for pink

253
00:10:05,578 --> 00:10:06,457
and green

254
00:10:06,658 --> 00:10:07,457
for blue.

255
00:10:07,898 --> 00:10:09,217
Based on her description,

256
00:10:09,458 --> 00:10:09,817
she fits

257
00:10:09,818 --> 00:10:11,457
the clinical presentation of tritanopia.

258
00:10:12,218 --> 00:10:13,537
So later I tested

259
00:10:13,538 --> 00:10:14,697
Zhou Quan's color vision.

260
00:10:15,178 --> 00:10:16,417
I found he sees, colors normally.

261
00:10:17,578 --> 00:10:18,537
What is this mess?

262
00:10:18,898 --> 00:10:20,097
There's yellow and pink here!

263
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:22,097
Don't you know I like things neat?

264
00:10:22,938 --> 00:10:23,577
Take it away!

265
00:10:23,898 --> 00:10:24,457
Yes.

266
00:10:25,418 --> 00:10:26,217
Therefore, he cannot

267
00:10:26,698 --> 00:10:28,337
be their biological father.

268
00:10:28,938 --> 00:10:30,097
So that's it.

269
00:10:30,458 --> 00:10:31,577
It seems the Fourth Concubine

270
00:10:31,578 --> 00:10:32,577
already knew the answer.

271
00:10:32,578 --> 00:10:33,817
Given her character

272
00:10:34,298 --> 00:10:35,657
she would privately approach Zhou Quan

273
00:10:35,658 --> 00:10:37,097
with some excuse.

274
00:10:37,338 --> 00:10:38,457
And he would believe her.

275
00:10:39,658 --> 00:10:40,937
After all, people in affairs

276
00:10:41,218 --> 00:10:42,097
always think

277
00:10:42,098 --> 00:10:43,097
they're the true love.

278
00:10:45,098 --> 00:10:46,937
You're truly clever and remarkable.

279
00:10:47,098 --> 00:10:48,577
Have you figured out how to handle

280
00:10:49,218 --> 00:10:50,417
the family head meeting in three days?

281
00:10:57,458 --> 00:10:57,817
Report!

282
00:10:58,218 --> 00:10:59,337
The Fourth Concubine is here to see you!

283
00:11:01,938 --> 00:11:02,457
I don't want to see her.

284
00:11:07,178 --> 00:11:07,817
Who sent you?

285
00:11:08,658 --> 00:11:10,097
Even when a judge passes sentence,

286
00:11:10,098 --> 00:11:11,657
they hear the defendant's plea.

287
00:11:12,658 --> 00:11:13,417
How?

288
00:11:14,218 --> 00:11:15,937
Are you sentencing me to death?

289
00:11:17,658 --> 00:11:17,937
Yes.

290
00:11:21,578 --> 00:11:23,097
What's left to say between us?

291
00:11:23,218 --> 00:11:24,457
I saw it with my own eyes.

292
00:11:25,458 --> 00:11:27,217
I tampered with the basin

293
00:11:27,338 --> 00:11:28,897
so the blood wouldn't mix.

294
00:11:32,338 --> 00:11:33,097
How did you know

295
00:11:33,098 --> 00:11:34,417
they'd do a blood affinity test?

296
00:11:36,098 --> 00:11:37,217
Three years ago,

297
00:11:37,218 --> 00:11:38,777
Master almost suspected us.

298
00:11:38,898 --> 00:11:40,017
The evidence that night

299
00:11:40,018 --> 00:11:41,417
was taken by Zhou Yimo.

300
00:11:41,658 --> 00:11:43,337
How could I not be prepared?

301
00:11:44,698 --> 00:11:45,537
Zhou Quan.

302
00:11:46,778 --> 00:11:48,337
We've known each other for years.

303
00:11:49,098 --> 00:11:49,777
Don't you know

304
00:11:49,778 --> 00:11:51,097
what kind of person I am?

305
00:11:51,818 --> 00:11:53,777
I don't leave evidence for others to find.

306
00:11:55,218 --> 00:11:55,817
So...

307
00:11:56,098 --> 00:11:56,417
So..

308
00:11:56,898 --> 00:11:57,897
Are they my children?

309
00:11:59,338 --> 00:12:01,017
The children are both yours.

310
00:12:01,938 --> 00:12:03,337
Set your mind at ease.

311
00:12:04,898 --> 00:12:06,337
Wonderful, Youyi!

312
00:12:06,818 --> 00:12:08,177
I was too anxious.

313
00:12:08,578 --> 00:12:09,897
I feared all these years

314
00:12:09,898 --> 00:12:11,657
I'd been just wishful thinking.

315
00:12:12,178 --> 00:12:14,217
Of course I know your feelings for me.

316
00:12:14,898 --> 00:12:15,897
Otherwise...

317
00:12:16,298 --> 00:12:16,657
how could I

318
00:12:16,658 --> 00:12:18,177
have borne you two children?

319
00:12:19,098 --> 00:12:20,017
It was the biggest risk

320
00:12:20,018 --> 00:12:21,217
I've ever taken in my life.

321
00:12:21,898 --> 00:12:23,657
Tomorrow is the family head election.

322
00:12:24,898 --> 00:12:26,577
You'll continue supporting me, right?

323
00:12:27,218 --> 00:12:27,577
Of course.

324
00:12:28,338 --> 00:12:29,817
The He family is challenging me.

325
00:12:30,338 --> 00:12:31,337
I hope

326
00:12:32,218 --> 00:12:33,537
you can quietly warn

327
00:12:35,178 --> 00:12:37,177
those opportunists for me.

328
00:12:38,338 --> 00:12:38,897
Rest assured.

329
00:12:39,418 --> 00:12:39,937
I will.

330
00:12:41,578 --> 00:12:42,577
With you here,

331
00:12:42,818 --> 00:12:44,217
I've always felt secure.

332
00:12:46,498 --> 00:12:49,137
[Zhou's residence]

333
00:13:06,578 --> 00:13:08,297
Everyone is present today.

334
00:13:09,098 --> 00:13:10,097
I hereby announce

335
00:13:10,938 --> 00:13:12,337
the Zhou family head election

336
00:13:13,018 --> 00:13:13,937
now begins.

337
00:13:15,178 --> 00:13:15,777
Everyone,

338
00:13:16,538 --> 00:13:17,897
I withdraw from the headship race.

339
00:13:27,778 --> 00:13:28,457
Ms. Lin.

340
00:13:38,218 --> 00:13:39,537
I'll be direct with you.

341
00:13:40,098 --> 00:13:41,017
I want you

342
00:13:41,458 --> 00:13:42,777
to withdraw from the headship.

343
00:13:45,778 --> 00:13:47,657
Have you lost your mind?

344
00:13:49,578 --> 00:13:51,657
Zhou Yimo should be racking his brains

345
00:13:52,418 --> 00:13:53,897
over how to possibly challenge me

346
00:13:55,218 --> 00:13:56,657
in tomorrow's headship contest.

347
00:13:59,298 --> 00:14:00,777
Miss Yinan's color perception

348
00:14:00,778 --> 00:14:01,697
is abnormal.

349
00:14:02,418 --> 00:14:04,097
She sees yellow as pink

350
00:14:04,658 --> 00:14:06,297
and green as blue.

351
00:14:06,578 --> 00:14:07,817
But Master Zhou and Director Zhou

352
00:14:07,818 --> 00:14:08,897
have normal color vision.

353
00:14:10,058 --> 00:14:11,377
Therefore Miss Yinan

354
00:14:11,418 --> 00:14:13,097
cannot be a Zhou family child.

355
00:14:16,658 --> 00:14:18,097
By your reasoning,

356
00:14:20,218 --> 00:14:21,577
who is the father?

357
00:14:24,698 --> 00:14:25,457
Not found.

358
00:14:27,098 --> 00:14:28,337
This is Zhou Yimo's

359
00:14:28,778 --> 00:14:30,097
gesture of sincerity to you.

360
00:14:34,098 --> 00:14:35,297
Why are you helping him

361
00:14:35,538 --> 00:14:36,297
so much?

362
00:14:36,578 --> 00:14:37,897
You don't actually believe

363
00:14:38,778 --> 00:14:40,017
he'll marry you, do you?

364
00:14:41,698 --> 00:14:43,337
In a certain sense,

365
00:14:43,898 --> 00:14:44,897
we're cut from the same cloth.

366
00:14:45,898 --> 00:14:47,577
We'd never entrust our lives

367
00:14:47,938 --> 00:14:49,457
to a man's hands.

368
00:14:49,698 --> 00:14:50,577
As fellow women,

369
00:14:50,578 --> 00:14:51,657
I truly understand you.

370
00:14:52,778 --> 00:14:54,217
In fact, I admire you

371
00:14:54,218 --> 00:14:56,217
because rising to the top is arduous.

372
00:14:57,338 --> 00:14:58,217
But given the current situation,

373
00:14:58,218 --> 00:14:59,897
your vulnerability is exposed.

374
00:15:00,578 --> 00:15:01,337
Struggle further,

375
00:15:01,338 --> 00:15:02,937
and you'll lose everything.

376
00:15:04,098 --> 00:15:04,657
Ms. Lin,

377
00:15:05,018 --> 00:15:06,417
if you withdraw,

378
00:15:06,818 --> 00:15:07,777
the Zhou family will always

379
00:15:07,778 --> 00:15:08,777
recognize your two children.

380
00:15:09,898 --> 00:15:11,297
The Zhou family's external businesses

381
00:15:11,538 --> 00:15:12,817
can still be fully entrusted

382
00:15:12,818 --> 00:15:13,577
to your management.

383
00:15:14,178 --> 00:15:14,777
We'll

384
00:15:15,098 --> 00:15:16,337
achieve mutual success.

385
00:15:16,898 --> 00:15:18,777
Each getting what we want.

386
00:15:25,098 --> 00:15:25,577
Deal.

387
00:15:32,658 --> 00:15:33,417
Farewell.

388
00:15:36,218 --> 00:15:37,097
Since Ms. Lin

389
00:15:37,098 --> 00:15:38,177
voluntarily withdraws,

390
00:15:39,098 --> 00:15:39,657
then we

391
00:15:40,298 --> 00:15:41,537
congratulate Young Master Zhou Yimo

392
00:15:41,898 --> 00:15:43,777
as the new head of the Zhou family.

393
00:15:51,658 --> 00:15:54,777
The Zhou clan elders

394
00:15:55,898 --> 00:15:57,697
have entrusted me with this duty.

395
00:15:58,218 --> 00:15:59,537
I pledge my utmost effort

396
00:16:00,218 --> 00:16:01,337
to restore our family's legacy,

397
00:16:01,898 --> 00:16:03,697
securing prosperity for generations.

398
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:05,297
Thank you, Young Master.

399
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:06,297
Thank you, Family Head.

400
00:16:09,338 --> 00:16:11,017
We pledge to share the boat

401
00:16:11,018 --> 00:16:11,937
and the destiny

402
00:16:11,938 --> 00:16:12,897
with our Family Head.

403
00:16:13,898 --> 00:16:14,857
Take your seats.

404
00:16:20,538 --> 00:16:21,417
Zhou Yimo,

405
00:16:22,178 --> 00:16:22,897
congratulations.

406
00:16:23,578 --> 00:16:24,457
Thank you.

407
00:16:24,698 --> 00:16:25,457
Ms. Ye.
